# Expense Operating Share Based Remuneration Amount

## identifier
de7496

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, of share-based remuneration expenses as determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.ShareBasedRemuneration.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
